MAN BRINGETH ALL INTO GOD

<table data-align="center">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 100%" />
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td>All things do love thee, Man, and thickly round thee throng:<br />
They run to thee because they would to God belong.<br />
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

 

