THE SPIRITUAL HUNT

<table data-align="center">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 100%" />
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td>Christian, the hounds will hunt thee well, both high and low,<br />
Wilt thou but willingly consent to be God's doe.<br />
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

 

272 (V. 110)  
ALL CREATURES RUN AFTER THE CREATOR.

<table data-align="center">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 100%" />
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td>Who the Creator hath, all things run after him—<br />
Man, Angel, Sun and Moon, Air, Fire, Earth and Stream.<br />
