<table data-align="center">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 100%" />
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td>Naught is imperfect, Man. Pebble is analogue<br />
Of ruby, Seraph not more beautiful than frog.<br />
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

 

