ALL IS THE SAME TO GOD

<table data-align="center">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 100%" />
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td>God listeth to the croak of frogs as heedfully<br />
As to the meadow-lark's sweet-throated melody.<br />
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

 

