THE WORLDLING IS BLINDED

<table data-align="center">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 100%" />
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td>Open thine eyes and see! Heaven lieth all unfurled!<br />
Thou seest it not? Then art thou blind drunk with the World.<br />
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

