<table data-align="center">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 100%" />
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td>God, God is All, All utterly,<br />
The lute-strings tremble at His touch;<br />
'Tis He that plays and sings in us—<br />
Is therefore thy performance much?<br />
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

