They'll tell you what it is—the dumb flowers yonder.<br />
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

 

288 (I. 290)  
LET GOD CARE

<table data-align="center">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 100%" />
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td>Who gives the lilics grace? the daffodils who reeds?<br />
Then, Christian, wherefore be so careful for thy needs?<br />
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

